 ies.\nWe'll be playing the following films\nSaturday\, April 4 –The Apar
 tment\nSaturday\, April 11 – The Color Purple (1985)\nSaturday\, April 1
 8 – Forrest Gump\nSaturday\, April 25 – The Bridge on the River Kwai\n
