UID:699f5fab4dacf581ff7de7ec@tpl.bibliocommons.com
DESCRIPTION:Practice your Microsoft Word skills when working with long doc
 uments.\nIn this class\, you will:\nUse Styles to effectively format\, str
 ucture and navigate your document\nCreate a Table of Contents\nUse Page an
 d Section breaks\nInsert Page Numbers and Footnotes\nInsert Web and docume
 nt links\nLearn about Microsoft Word's Accessibility features\nUpon comple
 tion of this class\, you will be able to format long documents\, such as b
 ooks\, reports\, and essays.\nPrerequisites:  Word Basics 1\, 2 & 3\, or e
 quivalent skills. Keyboarding and mouse skills are required.\nFormat: Hand
 s-on with demonstrations
