DESCRIPTION:Feeling crafty? Join us in the Youth Hub every Monday for Choo
 se Your Own Craft nights\, and pick an activity! Colouring\, painting\, pa
 per crafts\, and more! Do whatever YOU want to do\, while enjoying snacks 
 and other resources.\nThis program is part of Youth Hub service. Youth Hub
 s are a welcoming place for teens after school and in the summer\, where h
 elpful staff are always available. Free\, nutritious snacks are offered d
 aily. Drop by a branch with a\nYouth Hub\nor call the branch to find out 
 more.
LOCATION:Maria A. Shchuka\, Youth Hub
