DTEND;TZID=America/Toronto:20260610T153000
UID:695eea6594297d3600a3ecfe@tpl.bibliocommons.com
DESCRIPTION:This program helps people stay active\, make friends\, learn n
 ew skills\, and have fun. Meet new folks\, build connections\, and tell us
  about programs and services you would like to see in the neighbourhood!\n
 Join us and make some music! Express your creativity\, explore a variety o
 f instruments\, and sing your favourite songs. Connect with others and hav
 e fun! No musical training or experience needed.\nDrop-in\, all are welcom
 e. Call 416-393-7653 for more info.\nSnacks and refreshments are provided
  for all participants at 3:30 pm. Ingredient lists will be available at th
 e program.\nThis program is in collaboration with\nGerstein Crisis Centre'
 s F.R.E.S.H. initiative\n.
LOCATION:Sanderson\, Program Room
URL:https://tpl.bibliocommons.com/v2/events/695eea6594297d3600a3ecfe
