DTEND;TZID=America/Toronto:20260415T140000
UID:69977da7b0595799c09e088c@tpl.bibliocommons.com
DESCRIPTION:Are you feeling stuck in your job search? Explore the incredib
 le resources and expertise offered by ACCES Employment. Connect with an Em
 ployment Consultant to get tailored resume reviews\, invaluable interview 
 tips\, and a wealth of additional support. Book a free 30-minute appointme
 nt and embark on a remarkable journey toward your dream job\, like 1-1:30 
 pm\, 1:30-2 pm.\nPlease bring your finished resume/cover letter to the ses
 sion & your specific questions during the consultation\, for example edit
 ing your resume\, job search\, volunteer opportunities\, or Interview pre
 paration etc.\nPlease cancel as soon as possible if you no longer need the
  session before the program starts.\nSpace is limited. Help is available o
 n a first-come\, first serve basis.\nPlease arrive a few minutes early.\nI
 f no slots are available on your desired consultation date\, contact ACCES
  Employment directly for an appointment at\n416-443-9008\n(North York Loca
 tion) /\n416-921-1800\n(Downtown Location). Or visit\naccesemployment.ca\n
 The personal information on this form is collected by the Toronto Public L
 ibrary under the Public Libraries Act\, sections 20(a)\, 20(c)\, and 20(d)
