 tting projects while enjoying great conversation. We'll swap tips\, techni
 ques\, patterns\, yarns and more!\nPlease note this is not a program where
  formal instructions are given. However\, we are happy to learn from each 
 other and help each other out where we can.\nAll levels are welcome. Bring
  your own yarn\, needles and crochet hooks. Some material may be provided.
LOCATION:Hillcrest\, Auditorium
URL:https://tpl.bibliocommons.com/v2/events/696545e730cbd582eff4cdc7
X-SOURCE:Toronto Public Library
END:VEVENT
