DTEND;TZID=America/Toronto:20260509T150000
UID:69a85ab28d5e2d09336311f9@tpl.bibliocommons.com
DESCRIPTION:Welcome to the Romance Book Club\, where love stories take cen
 ter stage and every page promises a new adventure of the heart. Whether yo
 u're into slow burns\, second chances\, or enemies-to-lovers\, there's som
 ething here for every kind of romantic. Come read\, swoon\, and share your
  favorite moments with fellow book lovers.\nThe Romance Book Club title fo
 r Saturday May 11 2026 is\nRevolve\nby Bal Khabra.\nPlease note that this 
 book club is for individuals 18+.\nLimited copies will be available in bra
 nch for pick up.\nDrop in\, no registration required.
LOCATION:Maryvale
URL:https://tpl.bibliocommons.com/v2/events/69a85ab28d5e2d09336311f9
X-SOURCE:Toronto Public Library
END:VEVENT
