 ndling and movement\nLearn how to operate mouse buttons and scroll wheel\n
 Review parts of the keyboard including Letters\, Numbers\, Backspace\, Ent
 er\, etc.\nPractice clicking and dragging\nIdentify and understand various
  shapes of mouse Pointers/Cursors\nDemonstrate understanding of techniques
  through completion of Mouse Tutorials\nReview Mouse movements such as ope
 n\, close\, minimize\, maximize and moving of open windows on desktop
LOCATION:Deer Park\, Main Floor
URL:https://tpl.bibliocommons.com/v2/events/6996184b6583d22e3c0c64c5
X-SOURCE:Toronto Public Library
END:VEVENT
