DESCRIPTION:Learn how to enjoy movies\, documentaries and television serie
 s on your personal devices with your library card.\nKanopy\nprovides acces
 s to more than 26\,000 films and documentaries from a variety of filmmaker
 s and distributors\, including the BBC\, PBS\, HBO\, the Criterion Collec
 tion\, and the Great Courses.\nHoopla\nis a digital borrowing platform tha
 t allows users to download television shows\, movies\, and music.\nInfor
 mation Collection Notice:\nThe personal information on this form is collec
 ted by the Toronto Public Library under the Public Libraries Act\, section
 s 20(a)\, 20(c)\, and 20(d). The information will only be used for event a
