BEGIN:VEVENT
SUMMARY:Adult Afternoon Movie - The Wedding Banquet (2025)
DTSTART;TZID=America/Toronto:20260602T140000
DTEND;TZID=America/Toronto:20260602T160000
UID:69d81437129f12743837962d@tpl.bibliocommons.com
DESCRIPTION:Frustrated with his commitmnet-phobic boyfriend Chris (Bowen Y
 ang) and running out of time\, Min (Han Gi-Chan) makes a proposal\; a gree
 n-card marriage with their friend Angela (Kelly MarieTran) in exchange for
  her partner Lee's (Lily Gladstone) expensive IVF. Elopement plans are upe
 nded\, however\, when Min's grandmother (Youn Yuh-Jung) surprises them wit
 h an extravagant Korean wedding banquet.\nPG\,103 minutes\, Spoken langua
 ge Korean.\n*Subtitles for the deaf and hard of hearing when available.
LOCATION:Riverdale\, Program Room 1
URL:https://tpl.bibliocommons.com/v2/events/69d81437129f12743837962d
X-SOURCE:Toronto Public Library
END:VEVENT
