BEGIN:VEVENT
SUMMARY:Knit & Crochet Meetup
DTSTART;TZID=America/Toronto:20260430T140000
DTEND;TZID=America/Toronto:20260430T153000
UID:69b58b744dacf581ff81e82e@tpl.bibliocommons.com
DESCRIPTION:Unwind\, create\, and connect – one stitch at a time! Join o
 ur Knit & Crochet Club for a cozy\, creative gathering where yarn lovers o
 f all skill levels are welcome. Whether you’re picking up needles for th
 e first time or perfecting your latest project\, this is the perfect place
  to learn new techniques\, share ideas\, and enjoy great company.\nBring y
 ou current project or start something new\, swap tips and patterns\, and g
 et inspired by a colourful community makers. Expect a welcoming space\, a 
 lot of learning and endless creativity. Come for the yarn\, stay for the s
 ocial connections.
LOCATION:Beaches\, Program Room
URL:https://tpl.bibliocommons.com/v2/events/69b58b744dacf581ff81e82e
X-SOURCE:Toronto Public Library
END:VEVENT
