DTEND;TZID=America/Toronto:20260512T170000
UID:69ce83c82866a5b48845f760@tpl.bibliocommons.com
DESCRIPTION:You are tiny mice seeking adventure and renown in a huge and p
 erilous world of swords and sorcery. Will you and your companions prevail 
 over dangerous enemies many times your size? Or will it fall to others to 
 finish the job? In the likely event one of your mice should come to a grim
  demise\, you can quickly create a new one and keep on playing.\n*Registra
 tion is required. Ages 8-12 strongly recommended.
LOCATION:Lillian H. Smith\, Room B/C
