DTEND;TZID=America/Toronto:20260525T153000
UID:69ac6ae04dacf581ff804632@tpl.bibliocommons.com
DESCRIPTION:Join us to learn how grief comes up when caring for an adult l
 oved-one with health issues\, such as a friend\, partner\, family member. 
 Explore and discuss different types of losses and grief experiences that a
 re common for caregivers. Learn some practical tips for managing grief and
  loss and have an opportunity to meet other caregivers.\nLed by Social Wor
 kers Susan Anstice and Lois Didyk.\nNo registration required.
LOCATION:Don Mills\, Auditorium
