 ve fun!\nDrop-in. For ages 5-12.\nNote: Snacks are offered during the Afte
 r School Club for participants. Food may contain or have come into contac
 t with common allergens. Ingredient lists will be available. Snacks are ge
 nerously supported\, in part by donors.\nPlease note that this is a drop-i
 n program\, but space is limited. Spots will be given on a first come firs
 t serve basis to the first 20 children.
LOCATION:Malvern\, Community Room
URL:https://tpl.bibliocommons.com/v2/events/69d800f6ad384e40edb9ec49
