DESCRIPTION:Do you have questions about your tablet\, phone\, laptop\, ema
 il or an app?  Need help with eBooks or other online library services? We
  can help!\nJoin us for this intergenerational program that pairs teen vol
 unteers with seniors to answer your tech questions.\nDrop in\, no registra
 tion is required.\n3rd and 4th Tuesday of the month\, from 4:00-5:30 pm. P
 lease note\, in April\, program will run every Tuesday.
