UID:69b2fb1ec94c122f19bdcb4a@tpl.bibliocommons.com
DESCRIPTION:In honour of Asian Heritage Month\, Bendale presents​ a per
 formance of Bharatanatyam\, the oldest dance tradition of India. Originati
 ng in the Southern part of India\, the performance will highlight beautifu
 l music\, costume and story telling using hand gestures and expressions.\n
 Drop-in\nAll Ages.\nThe program will take place in the Auditorium located 
 in the basement. Elevator on site. If you have any questions\, please call
  Bendale Branch at 416-396-8910.
LOCATION:Bendale\, Auditorium - Basement
