DESCRIPTION:Join us for a musical storytime\, where you’ll discover your
  next favourite reads while enjoying an unforgettable performance from mus
 ician\nAmanda Goodburn.\nHosted in partnership with the Toronto Symphony O
 rchestra.\nThis program is suitable for children ages 4-8 years and their 
 families.\nDrop-in. Space is limited. Entry is based on a first come\, fi
 rst served basis.
