UID:696abaf8b0595799c096d200@tpl.bibliocommons.com
DESCRIPTION:Looking for something to do after school? Come out to our Afte
 r School Club and learn new things\, make stuff\, meet other kids and have
  fun! For ages\n6-12.\nDrop-in.\nUpcoming Programs:\nApril 14 - Colour or 
 Paint by Number\nApril 21 - To be determined\nApril 28 - Minesweeper inspi
 red game with Sphero\nSnacks are offered during the After School Club for 
 participants.\nFood may contain or have come into contact with common alle
 rgens. Ingredient lists will be available. Snacks are generously supported
 \, in part\, by donors.\nIf you or your child lives with a disability\, an
 d requires an accessibility accommodation to participate in this program\,
  please contact Accessibility Services by email\, accessibleservices@tpl.c
 a\, or voicemail\, 416-393-7099\, to make a request. Please contact us at 
 least three weeks in advance.
