DTSTART;TZID=America/Toronto:20260414T140000
DTEND;TZID=America/Toronto:20260414T150000
UID:699741014dacf581ff7c5c33@tpl.bibliocommons.com
DESCRIPTION:Join us for an informative presentation on the Disability Tax 
 Credit and the Registered Disability Savings Plan (RDSP)\, and learn how t
 o access these programs\, presented by CPA Canada.\nLearning Objectives:\n
 determine the eligibility criteria and requirements\ncompare which deducti
 ons are of greater benefit to taxpayers\ndiscuss the procedures to follow 
 when changes in medical conditions      occur\nidentify tax implications o
 f making withdrawals and contributions      to an RDSP
LOCATION:Northern District\, Main Floor Program Room
URL:https://tpl.bibliocommons.com/v2/events/699741014dacf581ff7c5c33
X-SOURCE:Toronto Public Library
END:VEVENT
