DESCRIPTION:Introducing Free Play\, a designated space for kids to hang ou
 t and enjoy STEM programs at their own pace. This program will run every T
 hursday night for the month of April\, excluding April 2nd.\nThis week we
  have Sphero free play! Learn how to navigate Sphero\, create obstacles an
 d solve challenges with the power of coding.\nDrop-in. Limited space.\nAge
 s 6 - 12
LOCATION:Bendale\, Auditorium - Basement
URL:https://tpl.bibliocommons.com/v2/events/69b1dbd5491b809c6f1fba09
