UID:6995cdeccbf1533ca5378d32@tpl.bibliocommons.com
DESCRIPTION:Join us for a monthly film screening of\nThe Wedding Banquet\n
 (2025\, Rated PG).\nFrom Director Andrew Ahn comes a joyful comedy of erro
 rs about a chosen family navigating the disasters and delights of family e
 xpectations\, queerness\, and cultural identity.\nDrop-in.
LOCATION:Runnymede\, 2nd Floor Program Room
