UID:6967cef8c719ac98c336e38b@tpl.bibliocommons.com
DESCRIPTION:Drop in to the Youth Hub every Tuesday and Thursday to play vi
 deo games. Play with friends\, by yourself\, or maybe someone new.\nTuesda
 ys will be Nintendo Switch days and Thursdays will be PS4 days.\n*NEW* Sta
 rting at 3:30 pm\, teens can sign up for a time slot to use the consoles. 
 If there is no demand\, gaming will be awarded on a first come first serve
  basis.\nThis program is part of Youth Hub service. Youth Hubs are a welco
 ming place for teens after school and in the summer\, where helpful staff 
 are always available. Free\, nutritious snacks are offered daily. Drop b
 y a branch with a\nYouth Hub\nor call the branch to find out more.
LOCATION:S. Walter Stewart\, Youth Hub
