SUMMARY:Digital Life Skills:  Online Travel
DTSTART;TZID=America/Toronto:20260520T140000
DTEND;TZID=America/Toronto:20260520T153000
UID:69cd79f19057005337d1d5e1@tpl.bibliocommons.com
DESCRIPTION:For people who have basic internet skills\, time and resources
  to pursue travel\, but want to learn about the online tools that can make
  it more affordable\, informed and flexible. We will cover major transport
 ation and accommodation websites and provide tips about booking online saf
 ely and securely. With these skills you can design a personalized vacation
  based on your schedule\, budget and varied interests! Resource handout pr
 ovided.
LOCATION:Northern District\, eLearning Centre
