 sues his arch-nemesis: the feline supervillain Petey the Cat. But the riva
 lry between Dog Man and Petey is upended by the arrival of an adorable kit
 ten clone of Petey\, Lil Petey\, who changes the game for both of them.\nR
 ated G\, 2025\, duration: 89 minutes
