DESCRIPTION:Find out how you can start investing for your future! Particip
 ants will learn how to save and invest in future educational expenses\, un
 derstand credit and debit while avoiding debt trap and good financial deci
 sions in an interactive workshop.\nThis program is part of Youth Hub servi
 ce. Youth Hubs are a welcoming place for teens after school and in the sum
 mer\, where helpful staff are always available. Free\, nutritious snacks 
 are offered daily. Drop by a branch with a\nYouth Hub\nor call the branch
