DTSTART;TZID=America/Toronto:20260609T183000
DTEND;TZID=America/Toronto:20260609T200000
UID:696abb606724c63d00ec9c9e@tpl.bibliocommons.com
DESCRIPTION:The focus of this program is to make quilts for donation\, usi
 ng fabrics that have been donated to the group for this purpose.\nParticip
 ants meet weekly to share ideas and inspiration while working on quilts. T
 here are no sewing machines at the library so any sewing is done by hand. 
 Most participants also work on quilts using their own sewing machine at ho
 me. Quilts are completed both as individual projects and as group collabor
 ations.\nNew members are welcome\, and will have access to the instruction
 s\, fabrics\, needle and thread required to contribute on-site to the curr
 ent group project.\nRegarding dates: The quilters will not meet when schoo
 l is out. E.g. March break and during the summer (July and August) and dur
 ing December break.
LOCATION:Jones
URL:https://tpl.bibliocommons.com/v2/events/696abb606724c63d00ec9c9e
