DTEND;TZID=America/Toronto:20260420T153000
UID:69a5c3006583d22e3c0dace3@tpl.bibliocommons.com
DESCRIPTION:This class will teach you how to prepare for the Canadian Citi
 zenship Exam using resources such as the Toronto Public Library website\, 
 Learning Express Library\, Brainfuse\, and the Your Citizenship Counts web
 site. You will also learn how to find your elected officials through feder
 al\, provincial\, and municipal government websites.
LOCATION:Northern District\, eLearning Center
URL:https://tpl.bibliocommons.com/v2/events/69a5c3006583d22e3c0dace3
X-SOURCE:Toronto Public Library
END:VEVENT
