DESCRIPTION:Join us once a month on Saturday to discuss the selected book 
 of the month. Share your thoughts and enjoy a lively discussion with fello
 w book lovers.\nThe Book Club Title for Saturday April 25 2026 is Listen f
 or the Lie by Amy Tintera. Limited copies will be available at the desk st
 arting Saturday March 28 2026.\nThis is a drop-in program. No registration
  is required.\nPlease visit the branch\, or call us at 416-396-8931 if you
  have any questions.\nPrint:\nListen for the Lie\nE-Book:\nListen for the 
 Lie\nE-Audiobook:\nListen for the Lie
LOCATION:Maryvale
URL:https://tpl.bibliocommons.com/v2/events/69a85d312866a5b4883fd2b5
X-SOURCE:Toronto Public Library
END:VEVENT
