DESCRIPTION:This\n program helps people stay active\, make friends\, learn
  new skills\, and \nhave fun. It involves peer-led group activities which 
 can include crafts\, games\,\n walking\, yoga\, and more. Meet new folks\
 , build social connections\, and tell us\n about programs and services you
  would like to see in the neighbourhood!\nOn Tuesdays\, join us for crafts
  (11am-1pm)\, a walk (11:15am-1pm)\, chair yoga (11:30am-12:30pm)\, and mu
 sic wellness (1am-2pm).\nDrop in\, no registration is required\nSnacks and
  refreshments are provided for all participants. Ingredient lists will be
  available at the program.\nThis program is in collaboration with\nGerste
 in Crisis Centre's F.R.E.S.H. initiative\n.
