DESCRIPTION:Golden Glow\nis a handcrafted beeswax candle designed with adu
 lts and seniors in mind\, offering a peaceful and soothing ambiance for an
 y room. Made from 100% pure\, natural beeswax\, each candle is carefully p
 oured by hand to create a clean\, slow burn that purifies the air and fill
 s your space with a soft\, warm glow. The gentle honeyed scent of beeswax 
 evokes a sense of calm and tranquility\, perfect for meditation\, relaxati
 on\, or a cozy evening at home.\nThis is a Drop-In program for Adults and 
 Seniors.\nNo registration required.\nSpace is limited. All materials are p
 rovided.
