 nd painter and author of\nAccidental Blooms\nas she discusses her latest 
 two books\,\nThe broken map home : escaping Korea : 1945\nand\nHidden Flow
 ers: A Memoir\n.\nKeiko's captivating story of resilience\, self-discovery
 \, and the power of community in the face of adversity seeks to inspire pe
 ople to view their challenges as an opportunity for growth. The memoir is 
