 navigating life's challenges.\nHidden Flowers: A Memoir\nwill be for sale 
 for $29.95 and\nThe broken map home : escaping Korea : 1945\nwill be for s
 ale for $22. Cash and card payment accepted.\nInformation Collection Notic
 e:\nThe personal information on this form is collected by the Toronto Publ
 ic Library under the Public Libraries Act\, sections 20(a)\, 20(c)\, and 2
