 ny camera. Throughout the workshop\, participants will embark on a journey
  to understand the allure and techniques of street photography.\nThis prog
 ram will be held in the\nActivity Room\,\nlocated on the first floor next 
 to the coffee shop.\n[Photo copyright Neill Sturgess Photography]
