 e benefits of using them\n- the differences between pre-installed\, free\,
  and paid apps\n- how to access and use the Apple App Store\n- how to eval
 uate\, download and use apps\nAt the end of the class\, you will have a ba
 sic understanding of how to install apps on your Apple device through the 
 Apple App Store.\nBring your own device: if you have an Apple device\, fee
 l free to bring it with you and follow along with the exercises.\nPrerequi
 sites:  None\nFormat:  Lecture with hands-on exercises\nInformation Collec
