 d breathwork and is filled with pages of creativity and activity. Kids and
  families can sit quietly and listen\, do partial poses or make up their o
 wn\, following our lead. It's ALL yoga! No experience\, mats\, or material
 s required.\nDrop-in.\nUnfortunately\, we cannot accommodate any large gro
 ups/daycares for this program.\nIf you identify as a person with a disabil
 ity and require an accessibility accommodation to participate in this prog
