UID:69a72311cbf6405d356934e9@tpl.bibliocommons.com
DESCRIPTION:Ready to turn your ideas into something people can’t ignore?
 \nThis workshop helps you master pitching through powerful storytelling an
 d deliver a confident elevator pitch that leaves a lasting impression.\nJo
 in us to enhance your pitching abilities and make a lasting impact on any 
 audience!\nRegistration required. Limited spots. This session is intended 
 for Young Adults\, but all ages are welcome.\nThis workshop is part of the
 \nYouth for Entrepreneurship program\nled by the YMCA of Greater Toronto. 
 Through hands-on sessions\, you’ll gain the digital tools\, financial kn
 owledge\, and creative strategies needed to build a business idea from the
  ground up.\n----\nInformation Collection Notice:\nThe personal informatio
 n on this form is collected by the Toronto Public Library under the Public
