 ames and vibe to some music.\nThe first session will be Bad Art Night! Whe
 ther you're a seasoned artist or a total newbie who can't draw a straight 
 line\, this is your moment to shine. Players will draw within the time li
 mit and the vote as a group on who has the worst art. The player with wors
 t art collection will receive some TPL goodies.\nDrop-in\nThe program wil
 l take place in the Auditorium located in the basement. Elevator on site. 
 If you have any questions\, please call Bendale Branch at 416-396-8910.
