DTEND;TZID=America/Toronto:20260417T200000
UID:69c71d87274a65e67a90f04c@tpl.bibliocommons.com
DESCRIPTION:Earth Day is on April 22 this year\, so join us and paint a cl
 ay planter pot! Each participant will receive one clay planter pot to pain
 t with acrylic paint. After the program\, you will have a beautiful painte
 d pot ready to house an herb or small succulent.\nAll materials will be pr
 ovided. Registration required.
LOCATION:Barbara Frum\, Room A
