 cience fiction fan Lloyd Penney. Lloyd is the current editor-in-chief of A
 mazing Stories Magazine\, the first science fiction-only magazine. We will
  discuss the editing process\, the 100-year legacy of Amazing\, and the jo
 ys of science fiction. A Q&A and booksale will follow the talk.\nThis even
 t is a tie-in to our current exhibit\,\nAmazing! Fantastic! Astounding! Sc
 ience Fiction and the Pulp Magazines\n.
