BEGIN:VEVENT
SUMMARY:Housing Help
DTSTART;TZID=America/Toronto:20260505T123000
DTEND;TZID=America/Toronto:20260505T163000
UID:69583000c719ac98c335c8bd@tpl.bibliocommons.com
DESCRIPTION:Drop in and work one-on-one with staff from The Housing Help C
 entre (THHC) to determine your housing needs\, connect you to other govern
 ment services\, and to match you with landlords across the city. THHC work
 s with both individuals and families in the City of Toronto to find and ma
 intain affordable\, safe housing.\nTHHC can be contacted at 416-285-8070.
LOCATION:Malvern
URL:https://tpl.bibliocommons.com/v2/events/69583000c719ac98c335c8bd
X-SOURCE:Toronto Public Library
END:VEVENT
