BEGIN:VEVENT
SUMMARY:Romance Book Club
DTSTART;TZID=America/Toronto:20260507T190000
DTEND;TZID=America/Toronto:20260507T200000
UID:69d98f88491b809c6f26991f@tpl.bibliocommons.com
DESCRIPTION:Welcome to the Romance Book Club\, where love stories take cen
 ter stage and every page promises a new adventure of the heart. Whether yo
 u're into slow burns\, second chances\, or enemies-to-lovers\, there's som
 ething here for every kind of romantic. Come read\, swoon\, and share your
  favorite moments with fellow book lovers.\nThe Romance Book Club title fo
 r Thursday May 7 is\nThe Book Tour\nby Emily Ohanjanians.\nPlease note th
 at this book club is for individuals 18+.\nLimited copies will be availabl
 e in branch for pick up.\nDrop in\, no registration required.
LOCATION:Brentwood\, Community Room\, Ground Floor
URL:https://tpl.bibliocommons.com/v2/events/69d98f88491b809c6f26991f
X-SOURCE:Toronto Public Library
END:VEVENT
