SUMMARY:Seniors Social
DTSTART;TZID=America/Toronto:20260421T100000
DTEND;TZID=America/Toronto:20260421T120000
UID:69a85f47491b809c6f1e0e02@tpl.bibliocommons.com
DESCRIPTION:Join us every other Tuesday at the Malvern Library for our Sen
 iors Social.\nEnjoy trivia\, bingo\, coffee\, chess\, and relaxed conversa
 tion in a welcoming and friendly space.\nParticipants can explore library 
 resources\, learn about programs offered across the library system\, and g
 et support navigating the TPL website at a comfortable\, relaxed pace.\nA 
 selection of books will be available to explore\, covering a range of inte
 rests and topics. It’s a great opportunity to meet new people\, stay con
 nected\, and have fun.\nDrop-in program. No registration required.\nUpcomi
 ng Dates (Tuesday):\nApril 7\, 21 2026\nMay 5\, 19 2026\nJune 2\, 16\, 30
  2026
LOCATION:Malvern\, 1st Floor Community Room
URL:https://tpl.bibliocommons.com/v2/events/69a85f47491b809c6f1e0e02
X-SOURCE:Toronto Public Library
END:VEVENT
