UID:69ac8cab2866a5b488408ff7@tpl.bibliocommons.com
DESCRIPTION:Join social policy expert John Stapleton to plan for your fina
 ncial future. If you are a low-income earner or advise low-income earners
 \, this program will help you understand:\nWhat Do Seniors Get?\nLearn abo
 ut benefits for Ontario seniors\, including the Canada Pension Plan (CPP)
 \, Old Age Security (OAS)\, Guaranteed Income Supplement (GIS)\n\,\nand Gu
 aranteed Annual Income System (GAINS).\nThis is a drop-in program. Registr
 ation is not required.
