  something new\, or revisit an old favourite in a safe and friendly settin
 g. Participants can also connect on a neighbourhood walk with a F.R.E.S.H
 . peer.\nDrop-in\, all are welcome. Snacks and refreshments are provided 
 for all participants. Ingredient lists will be available at the program.\n
 This program is in collaboration with\nGerstein Crisis Centre's F.R.E.S.H.
  initiative\n.
