 s. Mar. 12\, 2:00-4:00pm\nConspiracy\nby Michael Shermer\nThurs. Apr 9\, 2
 :00-4:00pm\nTrust the Plan\nby Will Sommer\nThurs. May 14\, 2:00-4:00pm\nC
 atch and Kill\nby Ronan Farrow **BOOK CHANGE**\nThurs. Jun. 11\, 2:00-4:00
 pm\nEscaping the Rabbit Hole\nby Mick West
