DTEND;TZID=America/Toronto:20260528T140000
UID:6988db3894297d3600aae83d@tpl.bibliocommons.com
DESCRIPTION:A meeting space for people and community organizations.\nEnjoy
  some light refreshments\, and informal discussion about services in the n
 eighbourhood. Get to know your local library staff and let us know what in
 formation and resources you would like to access at the library and in the
  community.\nEach month we will be joined by different community organizat
 ions.\nMar. 26 -\nHard Feelings\, Margaret's\, Woodgreen\, Yonge Street Mi
 ssion\nApr. 30 -\n519\, Yonge Street Mission\, Madison Community Services\
 nMay 28 -\nMarch of Dimes\, Yonge Street Mission\, Advocacy Centre for th
 e Elderly (ACE)\nJune 25\n-\nHard Feelings\, Yonge Street Mission\, Madis
 on Community Services\nOther organizations to be announced soon!
LOCATION:Toronto Reference Library\, Browsery\, 1st Floor
URL:https://tpl.bibliocommons.com/v2/events/6988db3894297d3600aae83d
X-SOURCE:Toronto Public Library
END:VEVENT
