UID:69ab319819c54125aa02a41c@tpl.bibliocommons.com
DESCRIPTION:A class on using Google's filters\, tools\, and Maps for absol
 ute beginners with little computer experience.\nIn this fourth session you
  will:\nUse Google search tools more effectively to find websites\, images
 \, and news sites\nExplore Google Maps to find addresses and get direction
 s for transit and road travel.\nUpon completion of this class students wil
 l be able to use more advanced search engine features and use Google Maps 
 at a basic level.\nPrerequisites: Computers for Beginners 1\, 2 & 3 or bas
 ic mouse\, keyboarding and internet skills\nFormat: Hands-on with demonstr
 ations\nDrop-in. No Registration is required
