DTEND;TZID=America/Toronto:20260516T150000
UID:69b08cca4dacf581ff81075a@tpl.bibliocommons.com
DESCRIPTION:Meet your 53 Division Neighbourhood Community Officers while m
 aking some wonderful creations to take home!  Free snacks and drinks are 
 provided after the craft\; ingredients are listed on the labels.  This pr
 ogram is presented by Toronto Police Services and is for children ages 6 a
