DESCRIPTION:A class on how to use a mouse for absolute beginners with litt
 le or no computer experience.\nIn this first session you will:\nObserve an
 d practice how to operate a mouse effectively\nUnderstand various mouse po
 inters and cursors\nReview basic keyboard functions\nUse the mouse for bas
 ic Windows functions\nUpon completion of this class students will be able 
