 ith\nEddie Lee\n.  Eddie is the founder and C.E.O of the consulting firm\n
 OneHub\nand has over thirty years of experience helping small and medium b
 usinesses grow and prosper.\nRegistration on the TPL website is encouraged
 .\nDrop-ins welcome until capacity is reached.\nFor more information\, con
 tact the North York Central Library\, Business\, Science and Technology De
 partment (4\nth\nFloor) at\n416-395-5613.
