 ople to become more aware of their soundscape\, inform them on noise regul
 ations\, how noise is managed by the City\, and talk about noise issues in
  their community. It will include the screening of the short film\,\nCitiz
 en Minute: Do You Hear What I Hear\nand a Q&A\, along with opportunities f
 or the audience to share their stories and the impacts noise has had on th
 eir lives. Led by Ingrid Buday\, founder of No More Noise Toronto.\nFree p
 rogram for adults. No registration required. For more information\, please
