 hey then apply using henna paste. Through hands-on experience\, participan
 ts can express themselves artistically while learning a traditional art fo
 rm.\nThis program is intended for children aged 9 to 12 years.\nOnline reg
 istration is required as space is limited.\nInformation Collection Notice:
