DTEND;TZID=America/Toronto:20260507T193000
UID:6941dba7b5ff47300056f5e4@tpl.bibliocommons.com
DESCRIPTION:Do you enjoy recipes and learning about food. Novice or chef e
 xtraordinaire\, drop in for an evening of culinary adventure.  Each month 
 we will delve into a different topic with lively and friendly  conversatio
 n. There will also be a selection of cookbooks to peruse and enjoy.  Last 
 year's book club created a 50-page recipe book to take home and enjoy.\nDr
 op In. No Registration Required.
