BEGIN:VEVENT
SUMMARY:Finding Recovery Through Exercise Skills and Hope (FRESH): Drop In
  Fridays
DTSTART;TZID=America/Toronto:20260417T110000
DTEND;TZID=America/Toronto:20260417T130000
UID:69496312c967cb41207dfcb2@tpl.bibliocommons.com
DESCRIPTION:This program helps people stay active\, make friends\, learn n
 ew skills\, and have fun. It involves peer-led group activities including 
 crafts\, games\, walking\, yoga and more. Meet new folks\, build connectio
 ns\, and tell us about programs and services you would like to see in the 
 neighbourhood!\nDrop in\, no registration is required.\nSnacks and refresh
 ments are provided for all participants. Ingredient lists will be availabl
 e at the program.\nThis program is in collaboration with\nGerstein Crisis 
 Centre's F.R.E.S.H. initiative\n.
LOCATION:Parkdale
URL:https://tpl.bibliocommons.com/v2/events/69496312c967cb41207dfcb2
X-SOURCE:Toronto Public Library
END:VEVENT
