  (January to June 2026)\nJanuary 28\n–\nThe Wager: A Tale of Shipwreck\,
  Mutiny and Murder\,\nDavid Grann\nFebruary 25\n–\nHunger\n\, Roxane Gay
 \nMarch 25\n–\nThe Rise of Wolf 8: Witnessing the Triumph of Yellowstone
 's Underdog\,\nRick McIntyre and Robert Redford\nApril\n29\n–\nFlash Boy
 s: A Wall Street Revolt\,\nMichael Lewis\nMay 27\n–\nValley of the Birdt
 ail: an Indian reserve\, a white town\, and the road to reconciliation\,\n
