UID:698e7ac094297d3600abf103@tpl.bibliocommons.com
DESCRIPTION:Join us on the second Thursday of each month for a friendly ch
 at about books.  We discuss a different book each month and copies of the 
 book are provided to book club members.\nBelow is our 2026 reading list:\n
 January 8-\nThe Beautiful Mystery\nby Louise Penny\nFebruary 12-\nThe Vani
 shing Half\nby Brit Bennet\nMarch 12-\nThe Unlikely Pilgrimage of Harold F
 ry\nby Rachel Joyce\nApril 9-\nBrooklyn\nby Colm Toibin\nMay 14-\nBanyan M
 oon\nby Thao Thai\nJune 11-\nEmpire of Wild\nby Cherie Dimaline\nJuly 9-\n
 Anxious People\nby Fredrik Backman\nAugust 13-\nThe Bandit Queens\nby Pari
 ni Schroff\nSeptember 10-\nThe Good Lord Bird\nby James McBride\nOctober 8
 -\nTom Lake\nby Ann Patchett\nNovember 12-\nEducated\nby Tara Westover\nDe
 cember 10-\nClear\nby Carys Davies\nInformation Collection Notice:\nThe pe
 rsonal information on this form is collected by the Toronto Public Library
  under the Public Libraries Act\, sections 20(a)\, 20(c)\, and 20(d). The 
 information will only be used for event and program registration\, deliver
 y and evaluation. Questions about how the library handles your information
