DTEND;TZID=America/Toronto:20260415T153000
UID:698f9559b48451fc3c029b65@tpl.bibliocommons.com
DESCRIPTION:Practice your Microsoft Word skills while creating a simple re
 sume.\nIn this class\, you will:\nFormat a simple resume\nPractice advance
 d formatting using Ruler Tools and Format Painter\nUse Grammar and Spell c
 heck tools\nPractice using Word’s built-in resume templates\nSave docume
 nts in other formats such as PDF\nUpon completion of this class\, you will
  be able to create an organized simple resume and access resume templates 
 with additional style options.\nPrerequisites:  Word Basics 1 & 2 or equiv
 alent skills. Keyboarding and mouse skills are required.\nFormat: Hands-on
  with demonstrations
LOCATION:Northern District\, eLearnining Centre
