SUMMARY:Youth Hub: Classic Tiramisu Workshop
DTSTART;TZID=America/Toronto:20260422T160000
DTEND;TZID=America/Toronto:20260422T170000
UID:69b04d85ec71a31f5b428b96@tpl.bibliocommons.com
DESCRIPTION:Learn the basics of how to make the classic Italian dessert\, 
 Tiramisu. Chef Yumiko will provide and explain all the ingredients and tak
 e the participants through a simple step-by-step process of creating a del
 icious ready-to-eat dish.\nFood allergy notice: Please be aware that food 
 will be used in this program that include dairy\, wheat flour\, egg and de
 caffeinated espresso.  The audience should be advised that certain food in
 gredients may cause allergic reactions in some people.\nThis program is pa
 rt of Youth Hub service. Youth Hubs are a welcoming place for teens after 
 school and in the summer\, where helpful staff are always available. Free
 \, nutritious snacks are offered daily. Drop by a branch with a\nYouth Hu
 b\nor call the branch to find out more.
LOCATION:Maria A. Shchuka\, Youth Hub
