DTSTART;TZID=America/Toronto:20260422T180000
DTEND;TZID=America/Toronto:20260422T193000
UID:69b9bc86b6c4ac1fedc66cf4@tpl.bibliocommons.com
DESCRIPTION:Are you a Newcomer? Want to practice your English? Join our FR
 EE English conversation circle\, hosted by WoodGreen Community Services.\n
 Accessibility\nLive or automated closed captioning\, sign language interpr
 etation\, intervenor services\, or attendant services are available upon r
 equest. Please submit your request at least 2 weeks in advance to:\ntpl.ca
 /accessibility-events\n.
