DTEND;TZID=America/Toronto:20260424T160000
UID:69b61aa181b67dfe32acab7e@tpl.bibliocommons.com
DESCRIPTION:Learn all about Adobe Lightroom CC\, an industry standard tool
  used by photographers to organize\, retouch\, and share their work. We wi
 ll focus on learning the workflow of the software\, covering topics such a
 s importing photos\, RAW vs JPEG files\, file organization\, retouching an
 d correcting our images\, and exporting and sharing our finished work.\nRe
 gistration will start 2 weeks before this class. Computers will be provide
 d.\nInformation Collection Notice:\nThe personal information on this form 
 is collected by the Toronto Public Library under the Public Libraries Act\
 , sections 20(a)\, 20(c)\, and 20(d). The information will only be used fo
