BEGIN:VEVENT
SUMMARY:Free Income Tax Clinic with North York Community House
DTSTART;TZID=America/Toronto:20260225T000000
DTEND;TZID=America/Toronto:20260516T235959
UID:699e6f984a9fd98b7f805d08@tpl.bibliocommons.com
DESCRIPTION:Available by appointment only:\nNorth York Community House\nis
  hosting a\nfree\nincome tax clinic for eligible individuals and families 
 at this branch. Please check below to see if you meet the requirements.\nF
 amily income limits include:\nOne person: $40\,000\nTwo persons: $55\,000\
 nThree persons: $60\,000\nFour persons: $65\,000\nFive persons: $70\,000\n
 More than five persons: $70\,000 plus $5000 for each additional person\nIn
  addition:\nThose who have T4 with income limits\nStudents with Tuition fe
 es paid receipt (T2202) or Bursaries/Scholarships receipts\nThose who are 
 on social assistance\nNewcomers\, such as\, Permanent Residents\, Refugees
 \, International Students\nWho is not eligible?\nThose who are self-employ
 ed or have employment expenses\nThose who have business or rental income a
 nd expenses\nThose who have filed for bankruptcy\nThose who are completing
