SUMMARY:After School Club
DTSTART;TZID=America/Toronto:20260507T160000
DTEND;TZID=America/Toronto:20260507T170000
UID:69d98d22ad384e40edba371f@tpl.bibliocommons.com
DESCRIPTION:For ages 6 to 8.\nLooking for something to do after school? Co
 me out to our After School Club and learn new things\, make stuff\, meet o
 ther kids and have fun! For the month of May\, participate in fun and cre
 ative challenges using LEGO blocks.\nSnacks are offered during the After S
 chool Club for participants. Food may contain or have come into contact 
 with common allergens. Ingredient lists will be available. Snacks are gene
 rously supported\, in part\, by donors.\nDrop in. No registration required
 \, but space is limited.
LOCATION:Fairview\, Room 201
URL:https://tpl.bibliocommons.com/v2/events/69d98d22ad384e40edba371f
X-SOURCE:Toronto Public Library
