DTEND;TZID=America/Toronto:20260413T200000
UID:698387dab0595799c09ac122@tpl.bibliocommons.com
DESCRIPTION:Adult Board Game Social – Tabletop Gaming Mondays\nJoin us m
 onthly at the Malvern Library for Adult Board Game Social\, a relaxed even
 ing of tabletop games and good company.\nHave a favourite board game? Feel
  free to bring it along and share it with others. Shorter and easy-to-lear
 n games work best\, but there is always room to explore something new toge
 ther.\nThe library will also provide a selection of board games for casual
  play. No experience needed. This is a welcoming\, low-pressure space to l
 earn\, play\, and connect with others.\nDrop-in.
LOCATION:Malvern\, 1st Floor Community Room
