DESCRIPTION:Want to learn to sew or would like a refresher on how to use a
  sewing machine? Our intro to sewing course will cover the basics of threa
 ding the machine\, basic stitches and more. We will be creating a small po
 uch. All materials will be provided.\nChildren under 13 must be accompanie
 d by an adult.\nRegistration is required\, and opens\non April 8th at 12:3
 0pm.\nNote: Your spot will not be guaranteed after 5 minutes of the start 
 of the program.\nInformation Collection Notice:\nThe personal information 
