UID:699f6037491b809c6f1c72a8@tpl.bibliocommons.com
DESCRIPTION:Learn how Google Sheets can be a useful free tool when you don
 't have access to Microsoft Excel. Topics in the course include how to cre
 ate\, save and edit Google Sheets worksheets\, adding and editing data in 
 a cell\, and more. Very similar in content to the Excel Basics 1 program b
 ut using Google Sheets.\nPrerequisites: Basic mouse and keyboard skills ar
 e required.\nFormat: Hands-on with demonstrations
LOCATION:Northern District\, eLearning Centre
