UID:69bc7c1867801235ed7350c2@tpl.bibliocommons.com
DESCRIPTION:April 15 is National Canadian Film Day. Join us for the screen
 ing of I Like Movies.\nLawrence (Lehtinen)\, an awkward and anxious 17-yea
 r-old cinephile living in Burlington\, ON\, in the early 2000s\, believes 
 that he is on the path to a legendary filmmaking career – but at this po
 int\, it’s only gotten him as far as a job at the local video store. His
