DESCRIPTION:Pastry Chef Yumiko Kobayashi leads this hands-on one-hour cupc
 ake workshop where participants will each mix\, pipe and decorate two cupc
 akes. Participants will learn primary techniques like piping with cream ch
 eese and buttercream frosting and decorating. All ingredients to be provid
 ed and prepped by the chef.\nFood allergy notice: Please be aware that foo
 d will be used in this program that contains gluten and dairy.  Certain fo
 od ingredients may cause allergic reactions in some people.\nThis program 
