DTEND;TZID=America/Toronto:20260418T113000
UID:69b596111e64afd01e621dc6@tpl.bibliocommons.com
DESCRIPTION:Create a Business Profile Microsoft PowerPoint presentation.\n
 In this second session\, you will:\nCreate a Business Profile presentation
 \nWork with presentation templates\nInsert and format tables and photos\nA
 dd Speaker notes and Print presentations\nUpon completion of this class\, 
 you will be able to create a simple Business Profile PowerPoint presentati
 on.\nPrerequisites:  PowerPoint Basics 1 or equivalent experience. Basic k
 eyboarding and mouse skills required.\nFormat:  Hands-on with demonstratio
 ns
LOCATION:Agincourt\, Learning Centre\, 1st floor
URL:https://tpl.bibliocommons.com/v2/events/69b596111e64afd01e621dc6
X-SOURCE:Toronto Public Library
