DTEND;TZID=America/Toronto:20260422T150000
UID:69c6d2d5b48451fc3c0baada@tpl.bibliocommons.com
DESCRIPTION:Have questions about your tablet\, phone\, laptop\, email or a
 n app? Need help with eBooks or other online library services?\nWe know ke
 eping up with new technology can be difficult! Our staff are here to teach
  you technology tools and concepts in a friendly and casual setting. Pleas
 e bring your personal device and any questions you may have.\n*Longer ques
 tions may be referred to a 1-hour Book a Librarian appointment at a later 
 date.*\n*No technology repairs at this event.*\nDrop In. No Registration r
 equired
