 mois d'avril nous allons discuter le film\nLe ventre de Bassima\n(Canada\,
  2024).  Le film est disponible sur la plateforme numérique\nKanopy\n.\nP
 ractice your French and explore the world of French-language cinema. Every
  month we meet to discuss a French-language film that you\nwatch at home\n
 before the meeting.  All levels are welcome. Please register as places 
 are limited.\nIn April\, we will discuss the film\nBassima's Womb\n(\nLe v
 entre de Bassima\n) (Canada\, 2024).  The films is available on the stream
 ing platform\nKanopy\n.\nInformation Collection Notice\n: The personal inf
