 to follow along.\nRegistration is encouraged on TPL website.\nDrop-ins wel
 come until capacity is reached.\nInformation Collection Notice:\nThe perso
 nal information on this form is collected by the Toronto Public Library un
 der the Public Libraries Act\, sections 20(a)\, 20(c)\, and 20(d). The inf
