UID:69cab8709057005337d152df@tpl.bibliocommons.com
DESCRIPTION:You are cordially invited to Northern District’s very first 
 Youth Hub Prom!\nJoin us for a night of music\, dancing\, and fun with fri
 ends. Jump in front of the photobooth and pose for polaroids. It’s a saf
 e space where everyone is welcome to relax\, celebrate\, and have a great 
 time. Dress however makes you feel awesome!\nVoted by you\, the theme has 
 been chosen:\nEnchanted Garden Under the Stars!\nAll teens are welcome! Dr
 op-in\, no registration required.\nThis program is part of Youth Hub servi
 ce. Youth Hubs are a welcoming place for teens after school and in the sum
 mer\, where helpful staff are always available. Free\, nutritious snacks 
