DESCRIPTION:Have you ever wondered about magic? Drop by the Youth Hub for 
 a workshop with WonderPhil to learn to perform easy but amazing magic tric
 ks with everyday items found around the home! Amaze your friends and famil
 y by discovering basic sleight of hands moves\, such as false transfers an
 d palming. Learn playing card tricks\, “mind control” tricks and more!
 \nAll teens are welcome! Drop-in\, no registration required.\nThis program
  is part of Youth Hub service. Youth Hubs are a welcoming place for teens 
 after school and in the summer\, where helpful staff are always available.
