UID:69cabd17b6c4ac1fedc918a6@tpl.bibliocommons.com
DESCRIPTION:In this 45 minute to 1 hour workshop\, participants will learn
  how to prepare a classic milk bubble tea\, including decorating and mixin
 g techniques\, as well as the breakdown of core ingredients. A classic lid
 ded cup and straw will be provided to enjoy the boba as you go!\n(**This p
 rogram uses food items that contain dairy**)\nTo secure a spot\, register 
 online. Remaining spots will be awarded on a first come\, first served bas
 is.\nThis program is part of Youth Hub service. Youth Hubs are a welcoming
