BEGIN:VEVENT
SUMMARY:Data Analytics Essentials Online Learning Circle
DTSTART;TZID=America/Toronto:20260415T180000
DTEND;TZID=America/Toronto:20260415T193000
UID:69b1845b4dacf581ff812680@tpl.bibliocommons.com
DESCRIPTION:Interested in learning about data analytics? Let's take a free
  online course together in a welcoming space!\nA\nlearning circle\nis a st
 udy group\, guided by library staff\, for people who want to take a free o
 nline course together in a supportive and welcoming environment.\nOrganiza
 tions all over the world recognize the value of analytics. Together\, we'l
 l learn about the essential tools used in this field.\nIn this 12-week lea
 rning circle\, we will work through The Data Analytics Essentials course f
 rom Cisco Networking Academy. We will explore the fundamental tools of a d
 ata analyst\, including how to:\ntransform\, organize and visualize data w
 ith spreadsheet tools like Excel\nquery data from a relational database us
 ing SQL\nimprove data presentations using business intelligence tools like
  Tableau\nWe will meet\nonline\nevery Wednesday evening\, April 8 - June 2
 4\, 6-7:30 PM (12 sessions).\nParticipants are expected to commit to the d
 uration of the course and attend sessions on a weekly basis.\nLearners who
  complete the course will be able to:\nearn a digital badge\ndownload a ce
 rtificate of completion
URL:https://tpl.bibliocommons.com/v2/events/69b1845b4dacf581ff812680
X-SOURCE:Toronto Public Library
END:VEVENT
