DESCRIPTION:Volunteer Toronto will help you discover how to get involved 
 as a volunteer. Learn where to search for opportunities and how to find th
 e best match for your needs and goals.\nThis session is great for youth wh
 o want to make a positive impact on our city.\nThis program is part of You
 th Hub service. Youth Hubs are a welcoming place for teens after school an
 d in the summer\, where helpful staff are always available. Free\, nutriti
 ous snacks are offered daily. Drop by a branch with a\nYouth Hub\nor call 
 the branch to find out more.
