 ore basic tools and use them to build your own 3D Music Note App Icon from
  start to finish.\nNote: Please create a free Spline account at\nspline.de
 sign\nbefore the session begin.\nThis program is designed for adults and t
 eens\, but children aged 10–12 are also welcome to register.
