UID:69b06fb56583d22e3c0e8cef@tpl.bibliocommons.com
DESCRIPTION:Want to enjoy vegetables you've grown yourself in your own bac
 kyard or on your balcony?  A\nToronto Master Gardener\nwill lead a demonst
 ration and show you how to get started to grow your own vegetables.  Get s
 ome tips and learn techniques for successful growing.\nAt the end of the p
 rogram\, vegetable seeds or seedlings will be shared with attendees\, whil
 e supplies last.\nPlease register online.\nInformation Collection Notice:\
 nThe personal information on this form is collected by the Toronto Public 
